CHOOSE A LICENSE BEFORE PUBLISHING.

Keel is intended to be free to use for personal or commercial projects, with no
attribution required. Two options that match that intent:

  - The Unlicense / CC0  -> truly no attribution, public-domain style
  - MIT                  -> permissive, but keeps a short attribution notice

Paste the full text of your chosen license here. If the landing page promises
"no attribution required," prefer The Unlicense or CC0 over MIT.
